      "firm_id": "standard_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition. The exterior shows visible scratches, several small dents, and some fading in the paint. The interior has noticeable wear, including some staining on the carpets and minor scuffs on the door panels. Mechanically, the car is operational but may require some maintenance in the near future.",
