    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and would best serve as a parts car or a major restoration project. The exterior shows significant neglect, including pervasive rust on the wheel arches, several deep scratches, and a cracked windshield. Mechanically, the engine starts but suffers from a heavy knock and a leaking head gasket, while the transmission shifts roughly between second and third gears. The interior is heavily worn with torn upholstery and non-functional electronics, including the radio and climate control. It is being sold strictly as-is.",
      "price": 5200.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
