    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional specimen that redefines the standard for pre-owned excellence. This vehicle has been meticulously maintained in a climate-controlled environment, preserving its showroom-quality finish since day one. The exterior features a deep, mirror-like luster with absolutely zero imperfections, rock chips, or swirl marks, protected by a professional ceramic coating. Inside, the cabin remains in pristine condition; the premium leather upholstery retains its original factory scent and supple texture, showing no signs of wear, creasing, or sun exposure. Every electronic component, from the high-fidelity surround-sound system to the advanced navigation interface, functions flawlessly. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, benefiting from a rigorous preventative maintenance schedule documented by a comprehensive, single-owner service history. The engine bay is spotless, and the undercarriage reflects its life of gentle use on fair-weather days only. This is a rare opportunity to acquire a collector-grade vehicle that looks, feels, and drives as if it just rolled off the assembly line. Includes all original keys, manuals, and a custom car cover.",
      "price": 44800.0,
